Holotype—habitus, ♂. A, B—habitus, dorsal (A) and ventral (B) view (without the tip of abdomen); C—left hind wing. Photos A &amp; B taken by Roman Hergovits.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<caption httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3367009/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="164" startId="9.[151,250,1914,1939]" targetBox="[158,1436,181,1870]" targetPageId="9">
