<taxonomicName authority="Vidlicka" authorityName="Vidlička" authorityYear="2019" box="[281,646,1914,1939]" class="Insecta" family="Blaberidae" genus="Lucihormetica" kingdom="Animalia" order="Blattodea" pageId="9" pageNumber="164" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="yasuniana" status="sp. n.">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[281,548,1914,1939]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="164">
Lucihormetica 
<taxonomicName box="[440,548,1914,1938]" pageId="9" pageNumber="164" rank="species" species="yasuniana">yasuniana</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
Vidlička
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[657,714,1914,1938]" pageId="9" pageNumber="164" rank="species">sp. n.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
Holotype—abdomen, ♂. A—dorsal view, B—ventral view; C—T8, T9 and supra-anal plate with cerci (dorsal view); D—subgenital plate (ventral view); E—right cercus (ventral view); F, G—left (F) and right (G) styli (ventral view).
</paragraph>
